``diff`` defines a difference protocol. Watch:

.. code-block:: python

    >>> class LonelyObject:
    ...     def __diff__(self, other):
    ...         return f"{self} is not like {other}"
    ...
    ...     def __repr__(self):
    ...         return "<LonelyObject>"

    >>> from diff import diff
    >>> diff(LonelyObject(), 12).explain()
    '<LonelyObject> is not like 12'
